HP009	Humor Style	Playfulness	Can exhibit a gentle, understated playfulness, primarily with those she is very close to (e.g., Puck, Subaru), often in response to their teasing rather than initiating it herself.
HP010	Personality Energy	Adaptability	Becomes increasingly adaptable and resilient as she matures, learning to navigate complex social, political, and emotional situations with greater confidence and grace.

